reviews.text: It is fun to walk around. The air condition is sufficient here. You may find variety of stores. There is a large super market on the underground.

It was a good place for ppl having dogs.
As they allow the dogs to walk in the shopping mall.
Also, you could also borrow the pet trolley to shop around, which is very convenient👍🏻

A nice shopping mall in San Po Kong which provides a lot of shops, supermarket and restaurants.  However, it is located near an industrial area and can not be reached by Mass Transit Railway.  But, you can reach there by buses, there are plenty of buses passing by and stop right in front of the mall.  Indeed,  driving your own car is the most convenience way to go there as there is a large parking lot with plenty of parking spaces. And, free parking will be offered if you spend a specified amount of money there.

reviews.text:
The Antoshimo cafe & bakery at San Po Kong offers this dessert for set lunch & set dinner for free! Super nice❣️
Antoshimo is a Japanese restaurant. Mainly provides Okinawa food. The food is delicious. Small restaurant but nice decoration. With air conditioning.

This place is surprisingly cozy despite its fast food style setting. It serves Okinawa style Japanese cuisine, at very reasonable prices. In the early days when the restaurant first started, they had limited options on the menu. But like other restaurants in HK, they have no choice but to offer a wider variety. Still, they managed to integrate a lot of Okinawa elements in the dishes they serve. Kudos to the operator. Must try: Okinawa donuts
Food is good, and dessert is what people come for.
Not much choice during CNY. We had the mini hot pot udon to warm our stomachs. And there is a donut with icecream comes along the hotpot set.
Not too fancy the food there...had a light dinner with snacks

它的午餐送甜品。本身午餐已經失去了它的特色,變得像是香港餐廳的午飯,港式飯盒價錢算合理,已經吃不到海萄葡,有點可惜。
因為有飯後甜品所以加分。。下次可以只點這個donut甜品,是非常好吃,雪糕下的donut是熱和脆的,很特別。
環境有點擠迫,坐得不太舒服,有點扣分,另外服務員好像總是忙著聊天,即使看到客人需要落單和埋單也是慢慢來,來這裡要有心理準備不能心急。

Good but pricy supermarket
